{"tid":35146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BANDAI金粉遊戲卡致敏 10少女手掌紅腫","createTime":"2016-12-12T01:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T16:42:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65b1e224413fa826942cab051d71f2303b5cb79e","tid":35146,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161211/280pix/1481466270_eda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161211%2F280pix%2F1481466270_eda0.jpg&h=a9d745d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBANDAI今日於荔枝角碧海藍天AEON舉辦AIKATSU!星夢學園(AK)跳舞遊戲聖誕活動，至少10名玩家購買遊戲卡，打開包裝後，手掌出現紅腫及皮膚敏感的情況，懷疑卡上有致敏源，當中至少8人須送院，包括年僅12歲患癌女童。任職網台主持的鈴子表示，今早偕朋友到荔枝角AEON參與BANDAI舉辦的聖誕活動，購買最新推出的AK卡，她指平日玩AK卡時都會先行戴手套，但礙於拆開遊戲卡包裝時比較不方便，所以今日未有戴手套。<br />\n<br />\n今早10時半，鈴子接觸過卡上的閃粉後，左邊手掌開始敏感，出現刺痛、發熱及腫脹，未幾右手亦有同樣情況，形容「腫起咗一舊，起碼2至3cm」。初時她不以為意，未幾有朋友亦開始出現皮膚敏感，當中更有人面部紅腫刺痛。<br />\n<br />\n至下午4時許，一名12歲患肝癌的女童率先無故「打冷震」，眾人覺得事態嚴重，於是要求大會幫忙召白車，將女童送院。大約個多小時後，至少有6名女子包括鈴子及其朋友相繼出現敏感，於是亦召救護車到醫院求診，並報警求助。鈴子稱，據悉尚有另一男子亦皮膚敏感要送院，故送院總人數應至少有8人。<br />\n<br />\n玲子引述醫生指，懷疑卡上的閃粉用了「劣質化學劑」，因而引起敏感，她經診治及服食藥物後已經消腫，不過有其他朋友須注射防敏感針抑制敏感情況，留在醫院觀察，而涉事的遊戲卡已交由醫生，再轉交到衞生署化驗。<br />\n<br />\n她向《蘋果》續指，自2014年瑞華行從日本引入AK卡後便成為忠實粉絲，又稱初時推出的遊戲卡質素良好，但至3個月前新推出的遊戲卡，紙質開始變差，不過未有想到今次新推出的遊戲卡會導致多人敏感，直言以後不會再購買抽包遊戲卡。<br />\n<br />\n有其他購買AK卡的網友在BANDAI的官方fb留言，要求解釋金粉脫落及皮膚敏感一事，並直指該批遊戲卡是「毒卡」。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，傍晚6時許接獲上址有人報案，指遊戲卡令手部敏感，6名女子(11至24歲)須由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\nAIKATSU!星夢學園(AK)遊戲卡是以收藏卡牌進行偶像活動的遊戲，玩家透過組合不同的衣服、鞋及飾物配搭出個人風格的遊戲角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56034476&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56034476%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161212&d=wf4GiX5tyj8uccFk1MzqeAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=f1352f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56034476%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161212&h=f0af0334\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56034476&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161212</a>"},{"pid":"41c34dfd755e7554f023e798444bf958c9288e38","tid":35146,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"笨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90c3ab226767abd8b6f0b2d1c1946674cb62b04","tid":35146,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"架佬產品靠害咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeac26fee18ddb535433e5a76ded72cf8fda36da","tid":35146,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>架佬產品靠害咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係真係以為日本製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f998d509f2361605b1497ab6dbf71346b8aeeaba","tid":35146,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874dd7d40b6bc6f724bb0340a8ac35f78501014e","tid":35146,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>架佬產品靠害咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係真係以為日本製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前萬變咭都有分日本版同港版，兩者紙質係差好遠，今次明顯笨大香港用左大陸廠造卡出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ce9c64a67eb2d0c8c6e69d4922a53ecce12dbf","tid":35146,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>架佬產品靠害咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208a10f10a72f56a270e6ddef1d5873d4713c5b8","tid":35146,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://v.wxjx123.com/?url=http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/393153772/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.wxjx123.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F393153772%2F0&h=9a85c62f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c502fcf9fb9cbcac9c7c19ff21edd95587a4525","tid":35146,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51188432a156e20adb09a3293dda76feed7000fb","tid":35146,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://v.wxjx123.com/?url=http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/393153772/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.wxjx123.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F393153772%2F0&h=9a85c62f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返支那啦五毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你食撚屎啦五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n( Show Blocked User - 5yen )"}]}